# Sensitive configuration files (excluded from dotfiles management)
# These files contain personal information and should be managed separately:
# - Git config (contains real name and email)
# - SSH config (contains server information)  
# - Claude config (contains user ID and project history)
configs/git/.gitconfig
configs/ssh/config
configs/apps/claude/claude.json

